      • addTask

        public void addTask(View view)
        This method is called when the user clicks the OK button. A new task is created based on user input. The task is added as an extra parcel to a return intent, and the activity finishes.
        Parameters:
        view - The view from which the user called this method

      • cancel

        public void cancel(View view)
        This method is called when the user clicks the cancel button. The activity finishes without adding a new task.
        Parameters:
        view - The view from which the user called this method
